
### Login (admin) - get access token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "testadmin@gmail.com",
	"password": "inipasswordadmin",
	"role": "admin"
}

# Copy the `access_token` value from the JSON response (response.access_token)
# and replace <ACCESS_TOKEN> in the requests below.

### Profile - requires Authorization header
GET http://localhost:8000/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Logout - invalidate current token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Admin Dashboard - only for admin role
GET http://localhost:8000/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

# Notes:
# - The app in this workspace seeds an admin user (see `database/seeders/DatabaseSeeder.php`):
#   email: `testadmin@gmail.com`, password: `inipasswordadmin`, role: `admin`.
# - If your app runs on a different host/port, update the URLs accordingly (e.g., http://127.0.0.1:8000).
